Date: Wed, 18 Jun 2025 15:12:08 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k:Add support for tx_stats

Add support for tx_stats and reset_tx_stats and also move
them under link sta

This patch combines Data path changes from below patches
504-ath12k-add-debugfs-support.patch
657-ath12k-Add-missing-per-peer-parameters.patch
714-04-wifi-ath12k-move-link-sta-specific-stats.patch

